## Images

Full rules: `docs/design-system/images.md`

- Brand/dev-owned images → `src/lib/assets/` → use `<enhanced:img>`
- CMS/editor uploads → `static/uploads/` → use `<CmsImage src="/uploads/...">`
- LCP / above-the-fold hero: `loading="eager" fetchpriority="high"`
- All other images: `loading="lazy"` (default in `CmsImage`)
- Wrap meaningful images in `<figure>`. Always include `width`, `height`, `alt`.
- Do not put CMS uploads in `src/`. Do not lazy-load the LCP image.
- Do not use GIF — use CSS animation or `<video autoplay loop muted playsinline>`.

## Typography

Full rules: `docs/design-system/typography.md`

- Default pair: Plus Jakarta Sans Variable (body) + JetBrains Mono Variable (code)
- Fonts are imported once globally in `src/app.css` via Fontsource
- Use `var(--font-sans)` / `var(--font-mono)` in CSS — never hardcode font names
- Do not add `<link rel="preload">` for Fontsource fonts (hashed filenames go stale)
- Do not use Google Fonts CDN links
- Paid fonts: `.woff2` in `static/fonts/`, `@font-face` in `tokens.css`

## SEO

Full docs: `docs/seo/README.md` · Page contract: `docs/seo/page-contract.md`

- Site config (domain, name, OG image, org) lives in `src/lib/config/site.ts` — it is the single source of truth.
- Every new public route needs the `SEO` component with `title`, `description`, `canonicalPath`.
- Every route (indexable or not) must be registered in `src/lib/seo/routes.ts`.
- Internal/admin/preview/draft routes must be `indexable: false` and use `robots: 'noindex, nofollow'`.
- Do not use `$page.url.href` as canonical. Do not hardcode domain in SEO files.
- Schema helpers are in `src/lib/seo/schemas.ts`. Only add schema when visible page content supports it.
- Run `bun run check:seo` before deploying. It fails on placeholder `site.url`/`site.name` values.

```bash
bun run check:seo  # validate SEO config and route registry
```

## What not to do

- Do not add Tailwind, shadcn, or any pre-built component library.
- Do not add `overflow: hidden` to `html`/`body`.
- Do not disable user zoom in `app.html`.
- Do not hardcode colors in component CSS when a semantic token exists.
- Do not build custom form validation — use Superforms + Valibot.
- Do not use plain `<img>` for brand or CMS images without a documented reason.
- Do not add `loading="lazy"` to the page LCP image.
- Do not add a Google Fonts CDN link.
- Do not commit `node_modules/`, `.svelte-kit/`, `build/`, or generated image output directories.
- Do not use `npm`, `npx`, `pnpm`, or `yarn` — this project is Bun-only.
- Do not commit `.env` or any file containing real secrets.
